author: Engineezy
description:
In today's stream, I’m switching to an old internet game called Fantastic Contraption with the goal of beating each level in the most overcomplicated way possible. 

Come hang out and help me overengineer solutions to what could be done in a much simpler way!

If you want to troll me and make my shop counter explode, head over to this link:

title: Overengineering Fantastic Contraptions | Engineezy Live ep.5
